\par\pard\plain \tx0\li720\fi360\sa120\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf7 After a strenuous Saturday working with a nonprofit organization, Evan\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s friends headed home, but the experience profoundly transformed Evan. Inspired by the selfless teen Diego, who chose to volunteer over typical leisure activities, Evan became deeply committed to the cause. His newfound passion led him to give up his entire Sunday, even forgoing his treasured softball game, to continue volunteering and making a difference.<!$Scr_Ps::1>}
\par\pard\plain \ql\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs18\b0\i0\cf7 <$Scr_H::2><!$Scr_H::2>}
\par\pard\plain \tx0\ltrch\loch {\f1\fs22\b1\i0\cf5 <$Scr_Ps::0>Leading Context:<!$Scr_Ps::0><$Scr_Ps::3>}
\par\pard\plain \tx0\li360\fi360\sa120\ltrch\loch {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 The day of volunteer work, cleaning up debris caused by the tornado, was complete. The Sun had just begun to set. In the previous scene, Evan befriended a young teen who volunteered his time and energy to the project without being asked. Evan took him under his wing, and they worked together throughout the day.}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 Katie had just watched Evan and Diego. The previous scene ended with Katie, Evan, and Diego headed to meet Sarah by the mobile office.<!$Scr_Ps::3><$Scr_Ps::1>}
\par\pard\plain \ql\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs18\b0\i0\cf7 <$Scr_H::2>}
