\par\plain {\f1\fs22\b1\i0\cf8 - Time: }{\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf1 <$Scr_Cs::2>Just before sunset.<!$Scr_Cs::2><!$Scr_Ps::4><$Scr_Ps::1>}
\par\pard\plain \tx0\li346\fi14\sb60\sl264\slmult1\ltrch\loch {\f3\fs24\b1\i0\cf8 - Weather/Environment: }{\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf1 <$Scr_Cs::2>Typical chilly fall early raving in central Illinois.<!$Scr_Cs::2><!$Scr_Ps::1>}
