\par\pard\plain \tx0\li360\fi14\sa120\sl264\slmult1\ltrch\loch {\f3\fs24\b1\i0\cf8 - Evan: }{\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf1 <$Scr_Cs::2>Evan was worn out from a hard day\loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8217\'92s work. However, he was filled with inspiration and gratitude for the experience he\u8217\'92d just had. He never knew that helping others in such tragic circumstances would be so rewarding. He was particularly energized by meeting the young teen volunteer, Diego. Diego had a similar family background, and they bonded quickly. Diego triggered a whirlwind of thoughts and emotions. He remembered how his father had abandoned him for another woman. But more than anything, he dreamed that one day he would be a good father, unlike his own. And in his dream, only one woman was on his mind - Sarah.<!$Scr_Cs::2>}
\par\pard\plain \tx0\li360\sa120\sl264\slmult1\ltrch\loch {\f3\fs24\b1\i0\cf8 - Sarah: }{\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf1 <$Scr_Cs::2>Sarah was impressed by Evan\loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8217\'92s transformation. He never ceased to astonish her. Although Evan was sweaty and dirty from a hard day\u8217\'92s work, Sarah found herself attracted to him, not because of his appearance but despite it. After hearing about Evan\u8217\'92s day and seeing his willingness to give up his softball game to help out more, Sarah couldn\u8217\'92t resist herself. She gave him a big hug and a gentle kiss on the worksite. Although most people had gone home, it was still a big step for Sarah.<!$Scr_Cs::2>}
\par\plain {\f3\fs24\b1\i0\cf8 - Katie:}{\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf1 <$Scr_Cs::2> Katie was exhausted, but you wouldn\loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8217\'92t know it by looking at her. She set aside her exhaustion and remained perky and happy.<!$Scr_Cs::2>}
\par\plain {\f3\fs24\b1\i0\cf8 - Diego:}{\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf1 <$Scr_Cs::2> Diego was happy and felt proud of himself. But his overriding feeling was hunger. This boy loved to eat. This was meant as funny, not as an indication of actual starvation.<!$Scr_Cs::2>}
