\par\pard\plain \tx0\li360\fi360\sa120\ltrch\loch {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 As the sun neared its rest behind the endless farm fields, Sarah\loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8217\'92s eyes caught the distant silhouette of three figures approaching the mobile office. The fading light cast long shadows, transforming the trio into mythical beings returning from some epic quest. Her heart fluttered as they drew closer, and she began to recognize their faces. Katie, Diego, and Evan, caked in the grime of a hard day\u8217\'92s work, wore the satisfying exhaustion of a job well done.}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 But her eyes lingered on Evan, and she couldn\loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8217\'92t help but zoom in on him. The sun\u8217\'92s last golden rays caught the sweat on his brow, making him shine like a character from a romantic poem. He wore rugged boots, perfectly fitting jeans, a light-colored T-shirt she gave all the volunteers, and an unbuttoned flannel shirt. Every piece of clothing seemed to cling to him just right, emphasizing his muscular form. As dirty and sweaty as he was, this image stirred something deep within her.}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 Her heart raced as his eyes met hers, and she realized with a jolt that she\loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8217\'92d never thought a man could look like that and be so sexy. The romantic feelings it invoked were potent, almost overwhelming, and she felt a blush creep up her cheeks as they approached.}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 The moment was pure magic, a snapshot in time when all the weariness of the day seemed to melt away, and all that was left was the connection between two people. The world fell away, and in that instant, it was just Sarah and Evan, two souls reaching out to each other across the space that separated them, bound by something far more profound than mere attraction. It was a moment she knew she\loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8217\'92d remember forever, a testament to the inexplicable pull of love.}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 All she knew about Diego was that he had appeared as a volunteer that morning, shadowing Evan all day, the information conveyed to her by Katie. In her hands, she held an honorary T-shirt for Diego, bearing the nonprofit organization\loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8217\'92s name, \u8220\'93Home Is Where the Heart Is,\u8221\'94 a simple token of appreciation for his selfless effort.<!$Scr_Ps::3><$Scr_Ps::0>}
\par\pard\plain \tx0\li720\fi360\sa120\ltrch\loch {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 [ As they got closer, Sarah started walking toward them. ]<!$Scr_Ps::0>}
\par\pard\plain \tx0\ltrch\loch \f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf7
\par\pard\plain \tx0\li346\fi14\sb60\sl264\slmult1\ltrch\loch {\f1\fs22\b1\i0\cf8 <$Scr_Ps::4>Middle:<!$Scr_Ps::4><$Scr_Ps::3>}
\par\pard\plain \tx0\li360\fi360\sa120\ltrch\loch {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 [ It\loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8217\'92s important to understand that children of all ages, particularly teens made Sarah nervous. Similar to the awkwardness she felt around people her own age, it was twice as awkward with children. But she was committed to doing her best when introduced to Diego. ]}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 [ Evan and Sarah gave each other an affectionate look as they came together. He knew she didn\loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8217\'92t allow PDA at her work, and he was filthy dirty and wouldn\u8217\'92t want to get her dirty by giving her a big hug. He settled for a loving smile. ]}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 Katie: \loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8220\'93Sarah, this is Diego. He did a great job today.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 Sarah: \loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8220\'93It\u8217\'92s nice to meet you, Diego. Thank you so much for helping out today. I have something for you.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 [ Sarah held up the shirt. Before giving it to Diego. ]}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 Sarah: \loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8220\'93All of our valued volunteers receive a free T-shirt.\u8221\'94 }
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 [ Diego received the shirt from Sarah and, being a polite young man, thanked her. However, he was interested in something other than the T-shirt. He turned to Evan. ]}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 Diego: \loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8220\'93That\u8217\'92s your girlfriend!?\u8221\'94 }
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 [ Evan wore the proudest smile a man can have. ]}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 Evan: \loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8220\'93Yep! She sure is.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 [ Diego was mesmerized by Sarah\loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8217\'92s beauty. Diego\u8217\'92s eyes widened. ]}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 Diego: \loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8220\'93You done good!\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 [ He then raises his hand to high-five Evan for his choice of girlfriend. ]}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 [ Sarah, Katie, and Evan laughed aloud at his remark. ]}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 [ Sarah nervously attempted to make conversation, wanting not to treat him like a baby but realizing he was not an adult. ]}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 Sarah: \loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8220\'93I know it was hard work, but did you have fun out there today?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 Diego: \loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8220\'93It was a blast!\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 Sarah: \loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8220\'93I\u8217\'92m glad to hear it!  What was the best part of the day?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 [ Katie chimed in. ]}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 Katie: \loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8220\'93It was hanging out with Evan, wasn\u8217\'92t it?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 Diego: \loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8220\'93Nope. The best part of the day was lunch!\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 [ Diego\loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8217\'92s comments had all three of them cracking up. ]}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 Sarah: \loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8220\'93Are you hungry?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 [ Diego\loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8217\'92s animated face told the story, but he also answered her verbally.]}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 Diego: \loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8220\'93I am starving.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 [ Sarah looked over at Katie. ]}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 Sarah: \loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8220\'93Katie, there\u8217\'92s plenty of leftovers from lunch today in the office. They are just going to go to waste. Sandwiches are in the fridge, drinks are in the cooler, and there\u8217\'92s still some snacks left in a bag.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 [ Diego\loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8217\'92s eyes lit up. ]}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 Katie: \loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8220\'93Would you like to grab some food before you go home, Diego?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 [ Diego was thinking, }{\f6\fs22\b0\i1\cf7 As if she had to ask.}{\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7  ]}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 Diego: \loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8220\'93Would I? Of course I would.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 [ Evan whispered something in Sarah\loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8217\'92s ear. Evan\u8217\'92s whisper led to Sarah offering something to Diego. ]}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 Sarah: \loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8220\'93We have so much food left over. Why don\u8217\'92t you take some home for your family?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 [ Diego acted like he had just won the lottery. ]}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 Diego: \loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8220\'93Really!? I ain\u8217\'92t gonna get busted for stealing?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 [ Sarah chuckled. ]}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 Sarah: \loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8220\'93Nope, you can have as much as you can carry.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 [ Diego pumped his fist in the air several times in celebration. ]}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 Diego: \loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8220\'93I am going to be the hero tonight!\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 [ Katie smiled ]}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 Katie: \loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8220\'93Let\u8217\'92s go. It\u8217\'92s getting dark.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 Evan: \loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8220\'93Give me a final high-five before you head out.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 [ The two high-fived each other. And then Katie walked away with Diego. ]}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 [Before they get too far, Evan shouts out.]}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 Evan: \loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8220\'93I\u8217\'92ll see you tomorrow!\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 [ Diego nods confirmation. ]<!$Scr_Ps::3><$Scr_Ps::0>}
\par\pard\plain \tx0\li720\fi360\sa120\ltrch\loch {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 He thanked Sarah profusely and gave Evan a final high-five before heading to the office with Katie. ]<!$Scr_Ps::0>}
\par\pard\plain \tx0\ltrch\loch \f0\fs18\b0\i0\cf7
\par\pard\plain \tx0\li346\fi14\sb60\sl264\slmult1\ltrch\loch {\f1\fs22\b1\i0\cf8 <$Scr_Ps::4>End: <!$Scr_Ps::4><$Scr_Ps::3>}
\par\pard\plain \tx0\li360\fi360\sa120\ltrch\loch {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 Sarah: \loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8220\'93You\u8217\'92re going to see him tomorrow?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 Evan: \loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8220\'93Yeah, I was talking to some volunteers. They said they were part of the Sunday crew responsible for taking everything down and packing it up to be transported to the next site or back to headquarters. I asked if they needed help, and they said they could always use help. So Diego and I volunteered .\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 Sarah: \loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8220\'93What about your software game?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 Evan: \loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8220\'93They can live without me for one game.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 [ Sarah looked stunned but didn\loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8217\'92t say anything. ] }
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 Evan: \loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8220\'93Sarah, thank you so much for today. I am a changed man forever. I want to volunteer as often as I can.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 Sarah: \loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8220\'93That\u8217\'92s wonderful, Evan. You have no idea how much that means to me.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 Evan: \loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8220\'93One more thing, Sarah, Guido, and the gang are headed back in a few minutes to guzzle down their well-earned beer, but I wanted to stay another hour possible to finish some cleanup in the barn. One of the guys said he would drive his car up and leave the headlights on so we could see what we were doing.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 [ Sarah\loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8217\'92s emotions were bubbling inside. Evan\u8217\'92s enthusiasm and dedication to her work warmed her heart and turned around at the same time. Evan continued. ]}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 Evan: \loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8220\'93The thing is, I don\u8217\'92t want to make them wait for me. They want to go home and party it up as soon as possible. Would you mind driving me to your place tonight?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 Sarah: \loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8220\'93\u8220\'93Don\u8217\'92t you wanna go home and party with your friends?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 Evan: \loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8220\'93Not tonight. I want to be with you. Today was one of the best days of my life, and I owe it to you. I know my clothes are dirty, but maybe I could sit on a towel or something, and we could throw my clothes in the laundry we get to your place.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 [Sarah\loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8217\'92s emotions were at maximum affection and maximum attraction. ]}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 She reached out and touched his arm, her expression one of genuine admiration. \loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8220\'93Evan, every time I think I\u8217\'92ve figured you out, you astonish me again. Giving up your Sunday, your friends, all for this cause, and for us... it\u8217\'92s amazing. }
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 [ They gazed longingly into each other\loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8217\'92s eyes. ]}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 Evan: \loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8220\'93I wish I weren\u8217\'92t so dirty, and we weren\u8217\'92t at your work. I want to kiss you so badly right now.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 [ Evan barely finished his thought. Sarah gently placed her hands on either side of his face and decided to break her PDA rule. ]}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 Sarah: \loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8220\'93Screw it!\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 [ As she held his face with her hands, she gave Evan a long soft sensual kiss.]<!$Scr_Ps::3><$Scr_Ps::0>}
